Title: Kanaka
Actors: Duniya Vijay, Haripriya, Manvitha Harish, P. Ravi Shankar
Plot: Kanaka is a Kannada movie starring Duniya Vijay, Harripriya and Manvitha Harish in prominent roles. The cast also includes Rangayana Raghu and Sadhu Kokila. It is a family drama directed and produced by R. Chandru.
